If you want to know about the quality of this DVD then have no fears, it is a very good job.  It is probably helped by the fact that it was shot in greytones giving it the feel of the original pulp novels.  There is some color when women are show or the color red is shown, these colors hold up well and dont bleed.  The picture quality remains constant and the framing is good throughout.  

I heartily recommend this download, of course I will buy the DVD when it comes out for all the bonus features and yes, the quality improvement but in the interim 6-8 months before this movie is released I find this DVD to be a suitable viewing.

Thanks to everyone involved with bringing this download to Pirate Bay.
